title: About Project
description: is a modern, out-of-the-box middle and backend solution that adopts the latest technology stack, including cutting-edge technologies such as Vue 3.0, Vite, TailwindCSS and TypeScript, with strict code specifications and rich configuration options, aiming to provide ready-to-use solutions and rich examples for the development of medium and large projects. At the same time, it is also an excellent example for learning and in-depth frontend technology.
